Batman: Arkham Origins Blackgate - Deluxe Edition amplifies the 2.5-D game

the storyline of the console version and discover more details of the Dark
Knight's past. Featuring stealth gameplay, free-flow combat, and Batman's
famed arsenal of gadgets, the genuine Arkham experience is reproduced in a
deep, action packed side-scrolling adventure.
